60
00:06:51,980 --> 00:06:54,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia akan menjadi suamiku.</font>

61
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar, bukan?</font>

62
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:12,060
