77
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:32,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergi.</font>

78
00:08:39,950 --> 00:08:42,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Aigoo.</font>

79
00:08:44,260 --> 00:08:47,160
