85
00:09:13,020 --> 00:09:14,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Terbaik di Goryeo.</font>

86
00:09:14,690 --> 00:09:17,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Kaldu ini kaya rasa dan manis.</font>

87
00:09:18,290 --> 00:09:20,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini akan membuatmu berenergi.</font>

88
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:26,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia di sini.</font>

89
00:09:35,910 --> 00:09:38,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Saudaraku./ Saudaraku!</font>

90
00:09:40,010 --> 00:09:42,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kau
lakukan selama ini?</font>

91
00:09:42,010 --> 00:09:43,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau jauh lebih tampan.</font>

92
00:09:43,780 --> 00:09:47,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang terjadi padamu?
Kau kehilangan berat badan.</font>

93
