94
00:09:49,660 --> 00:09:51,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang mereka lakukan?</font>

95
00:09:53,130 --> 00:09:54,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Entahlah.</font>

96
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:56,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Kesini.</font>

97
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:58,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka terlalu...</font>

98
