berita buruk.</i></font>

113
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:49,650
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Pengawal Raja...</i></font>

114
00:10:49,650 --> 00:10:51,780
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...memiliki lebih banyak makanan dan senjata
daripada mereka,</i></font>

115
00:10:51,780 --> 00:10:54,620
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...tapi barak pangkalan lain seperti...</i></font>

116
00:10:54,620 --> 00:10:56,790
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...tentara Eungyang tidak pernah dipasok.</i></font>

117
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:58,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka memiliki sedikit makanan,
pakaian,</font>

118
00:10:59,490 --> 00:11:00,690
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan senjata.</font>

119
00:11:01,060 --> 00:11:04,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Ruang Perburuan mereka memiliki hak untuk
mendistribusikan persediaan.</font>

120
00:11:04,830 --> 00:11:07,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka adalah pengawal Apamama
dan orang-orang jahat.</font>

121
00:11:07,270 --> 00:11:10,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka menjual
persediaan di pasar,</font>

122
00:11:10,140 --> 00:11:13,410
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan tentara diberi makan biji-bijian
yang sudah lama.</font>

123
00:11:13,410 --> 00:11:15,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukalah karung,</font>

124
00:11:15,470 --> 00:11:17,240
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan akan keluar
cacing dan kutu.</font>

125
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:20,580
<font color=#FFFF00>"Mereka memberi kita
protein dengan gandum."</font>

126
00:11:20,580 --> 00:11:21,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah yang mereka pikirkan.</font>

127
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:27,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi kadang-kadang,</font>

128
00:11:27,750 --> 00:11:30,020
<font color=#FFFF00>...agar mereka bisa makan,</font>

129
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:33,230
<font color=#FFFF00>...mereka terpaksa mencuri.</font>

130
00:11:33,830 --> 00:11:36,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka melepas seragamnya, dan
