131
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:39,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa mungkin.../
Mereka mencuri milik Pengawal Raja.</font>

132
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:41,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Para Komandan menutup mata mereka.</font>

133
00:11:41,530 --> 00:11:42,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Dengan bantuannya,</font>

134
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:46,010
