135
00:11:46,740 --> 00:11:47,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

136
00:11:48,470 --> 00:11:50,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Pengawal kami cukup terkenal.</font>

137
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:51,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Sangat terkenal.</font>

138
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:53,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka sangat terampil.</font>

139
00:11:54,180 --> 00:11:55,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Seberapa bagus mereka?</font>

140
00:11:55,410 --> 00:11:58,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka berpindah seperti bayangan.
