141
00:11:58,480 --> 00:11:59,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah mengapa...</font>

142
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:01,590
<font color=#FFFF00>...kami disebut bayangan.</font>

143
00:12:01,590 --> 00:12:04,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Raja mengirim orang-orang
terbaiknya untuk melacak mereka.</font>

144
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:06,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi dia tidak
menemukan bayangannya.</font>

145
00:12:06,930 --> 00:12:08,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah mengapa...</font>

146
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:10,500
<font color=#FFFF00>...kami disebut bayangan.</font>

147
00:12:39,830 --> 00:12:42,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Malam ini, kita makan pangsit daging./
Pangsit kimchi.</font>

148
00:12:42,930 --> 00:12:45,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Pangsit daging./
Kita sudah makan pangsit daging kemarin.</font>

149
00:12:45,970 --> 00:12:47,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin makan daging lagi.</font>

150
00:12:47,730 --> 00:12:49,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sangat egois.</font>

151
00:12:52,340 --> 00:12:53,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Pencuri.</font>

152
00:12:54,110 --> 00:12:55,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Tangkap pencuri ini.</font>

153
00:12:56,110 --> 00:12:58,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir!/
Tidak.</font>

154
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Serang!</font>

155
00:13:13,060 --> 00:13:14,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa kau?</font>

156
00:13:14,990 --> 00:13:16,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau...</font>

157
00:13:17,060 --> 00:13:19,270
<font color=#FFFF00>...pernah mendengar
pengawal bayangan?</font>

158
00:13:33,910 --> 00:13:35,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Sial.</font>

159
00:13:43,020 --> 00:13:45,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami akan menyandera teman-temanmu.</font>

160
00:13:45,930 --> 00:13:47,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Beritahu Komandanmu.</font>

161
00:13:47,390 --> 00:13:49,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika dia tidak menemui
kami hari ini,</font>

162
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:51,060
<font color=#FFFF00>...maka Pengawal Raja akan menemuimu.</font>

163
00:13:51,060 --> 00:13:54,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami hanya pencuri.
Kami tidak memiliki Komandan.</font>

164
00:13:54,070 --> 00:13:55,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yakin kau punya.</font>

165
00:13:56,340 --> 00:13:58,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Komandan Tentara Eungyang.</font>

166
00:13:59,670 --> 00:14:00,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika Tuanku...</font>

167
00:14:01,940 --> 00:14:04,910
<font color=#FFFF00>...mendengar apa yang terjadi,
dia pasti akan bingung.</font>

168
00:14:05,640 --> 00:14:07,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentara Eungyang berpakaian
sebagai pencuri...</font>

169
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:09,780
